{"tid":1717939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"論「磚」用途","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T17:34:16.000Z","uid":309305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a72de3e54414569219cea0b9cebda64573a9bf3a","tid":1717939,"uid":309305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"今日討論下磚嘅用法<br />\n<br />\n1.扔<br />\n2.road block<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日打機見啲磚就咁散晒喺地下好似唔係幾有用<br />\n至少我冇見過有人打仗可以散雜物喺地下就阻到對家<br />\n<br />\n既然我地有沙有土有泥有水有磚<br />\n乜建築材料都有<br />\n最重要係有時間<br />\n點解冇人諗過可以喺啲據點起啲更有意義嘅建築<br />\n<br />\neg 城牆&gt;&gt;&gt;直接block一條路 設立據點 <br />\n戰壕&gt;&gt;&gt;讀過WWI都知幾有用<br />\n磚屋&gt;&gt;&gt;遮視線,生產魔法等<br />\n<br />\n當然以上都係建立喺有足夠嘅材料底下先用<br />\n<br />\n依我所見大家都係未夠lv<br />\n太散亂 <br />\n祝各位早日打爆機<br />\n<br />\n以下繼續討論各種攻略"},{"pid":"93705c87439a3899ab04e161dd5ae279a674a851","tid":1717939,"uid":309305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:22:42.000Z","msg":"唉p牌自推"},{"pid":"accd5ab114a9cd474e340320d0d40483acac9c18","tid":1717939,"uid":309305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:23:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5150aa0edf679e2114ddd1f499b1f4d569dfbb3b","tid":1717939,"uid":309305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:34:03.000Z","msg":"沉咗"},{"pid":"19fae1676d2c3cf8c4713eba2c997d392cb7c4af","tid":1717939,"uid":309305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:34:16.000Z","msg":"88"}]}